{"tid":1104414,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食完PP 酵素第二朝即刻起身痾屎","createTime":"2019-04-13T06:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:32:30.000Z","uid":165939,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"44e5a1a6470e122d737bbf00bc7ea40d2a5b20d1","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"見到ig shop 最近好多人賣呢隻PP 酵素，吹到可以取代以前所有減肥產品（遲啲又有新嘢嗰陣會唔會又取代埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n不過我都忍唔住買兩盒試下，佢一盒一個星期份量，早晚各一包。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚食咗第一包，同埋今朝都食咗一包，跟住今日諗住買早餐嗰陣突然好急屎，平時冇食開酵素，唔知其他係點。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個暫時都算係幾溫和，再係到報告進度觀察下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果work 嘅睇下遲啲有冇人有興趣夾份，佢買得多可以平啲，但自己目標諗住睇下有冇可能減到10~20磅。<br />\n<br />\n不過真心一路食酵素都唔係長遠，所以都會配合輕量運動同食少啲油膩嘢再睇下點先<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 55kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (未開始食）"},{"pid":"6eea72728bca6560d2aae418f9811e7f4667946f","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"繼續Day 1: 17:00 痾第二次屎，但唔係肚痾咁痾，正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f8091dad9971d3546b174a456c64986cf2e213","tid":1104414,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"有無圖?"},{"pid":"171d5d5f823b3ae8f81cdc36d5f6b21ada807076","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"12f8091dad9971d3546b174a456c64986cf2e213","tid":1104414,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"有無圖?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"你想要咩圖？痾屎圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己search 啦，po 埋圖會唔會太過打手味濃<br />\n同埋我未試清楚，過多幾日睇下有冇輕先<br />\n真係好嘅先再睇下有冇ching 一齊夾下"},{"pid":"ed2a191a916595e66ab812d7c7c8898d2af9021a","tid":1104414,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"等睇兩星期之後體重"},{"pid":"c849758529f55c74719f497987195c9556fd13cd","tid":1104414,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"你絲打？"},{"pid":"dc1fb73bb17d4fb72cd365ad409cfc6a3d5e64d1","tid":1104414,"uid":128342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"夾份 定係你打算做埋d所謂 下線 代理<br />\n叫人俾錢買你products先"},{"pid":"6e8907ae0fdc2862fc1d907d1a8cfa311e5907b6","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"想知邊個咁得閒逐個comment 負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2609de40e5a613318c00858ee1ffb68df4f0748","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc1fb73bb17d4fb72cd365ad409cfc6a3d5e64d1","tid":1104414,"uid":128342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"夾份 定係你打算做埋d所謂 下線 代理<br />\n叫人俾錢買你products先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"邊有時間做埋呢啲代理，吃力不討好"},{"pid":"75802edc087363fefdd108a233a7853e3f1e1908","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c849758529f55c74719f497987195c9556fd13cd","tid":1104414,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"你絲打？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"有咩關係"},{"pid":"440e5a24ce995d374694274049b303da81687eb1","tid":1104414,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed2a191a916595e66ab812d7c7c8898d2af9021a","tid":1104414,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"等睇兩星期之後體重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"其實平時都唔係冇屎痾，諗緊係咪真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a8cabe89b34ed4f988e9bd3bda942b5c43d8b2","tid":1104414,"uid":128342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl